<h3>Setting up Nunjucks views and paths</h3>
<p>Below is an example setup using express configure views:</p>

<pre><code>
nunjucks.configure('node_modules/govuk-frontend/components', {
  autoescape: true,
  cache: false,
  express: app
})
</code></pre>

